# **Privacy Policy for Adepa Radio Android App**

Effective Date: 9th June, 2025

Adepa Radio ("we", "our", or "us") values the privacy of our users and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Android mobile application ("Adepa Radio App").

Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By using the app, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. If you do not agree with any part of this policy, please do not use the Adepa Radio App.

